 34544	real_T Ccontroller_ballcatcher_inv_kin::controller_ballcatcher_inv_kin_norm (const real_T x[3])
 34545	{
 34546	  real_T y;
 34547	  real_T scale;
 34548	  real_T absxk;
 34549	  real_T t;
 34550	  scale = 3.3121686421112381E-170;
 34551	  absxk = std::abs(x[0]);
 34552	  if (absxk > 3.3121686421112381E-170) {
 34553	    y = 1.0;
 34554	    scale = absxk;
 34555	  } else {
 34556	    t = absxk / 3.3121686421112381E-170;
 34557	    y = t * t;
 34558	  }
 34559	
 34560	  absxk = std::abs(x[1]);
 34561	  if (absxk > scale) {
 34562	    t = scale / absxk;
 34563	    y = y * t * t + 1.0;
 34564	    scale = absxk;
 34565	  } else {
 34566	    t = absxk / scale;
 34567	    y += t * t;
 34568	  }
 34569	
 34570	  absxk = std::abs(x[2]);
 34571	  if (absxk > scale) {
 34572	    t = scale / absxk;
 34573	    y = y * t * t + 1.0;
 34574	    scale = absxk;
 34575	  } else {
 34576	    t = absxk / scale;
 34577	    y += t * t;
 34578	  }
 34579	
 34580	  return scale * std::sqrt(y);
 34581	}

 34583	void Ccontroller_ballcatcher_inv_kin::controller_ballcatcher_inv_kin_mldivide (const real_T A[16], real_T B[16])
 34584	{
 34585	  int32_T ip;
 34586	  real_T b_A[16];
 34587	  int8_T ipiv[4];
 34588	  int32_T j;
 34589	  int32_T ix;
 34590	  real_T smax;
 34591	  real_T s;
 34592	  int32_T k;
 34593	  int32_T iy;
 34594	  int32_T c_ix;
 34595	  int32_T d;
 34596	  int32_T ijA;
 34597	  memcpy(&b_A[0], &A[0], sizeof(real_T) << 4U);
 34598	  ipiv[0] = 1;
 34599	  ipiv[1] = 2;
 34600	  ipiv[2] = 3;
 34601	  ipiv[3] = 4;
 34602	  for (j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
 34603	    ip = j * 5;
 34604	    iy = 0;
 34605	    ix = ip;
 34606	    smax = std::abs(b_A[ip]);
 34607	    for (k = 2; k <= 4 - j; k++) {
 34608	      ix++;
 34609	      s = std::abs(b_A[ix]);
 34610	      if (s > smax) {
 34611	        iy = k - 1;
 34612	        smax = s;
 34613	      }
 34614	    }
 34615	
 34616	    if (b_A[ip + iy] != 0.0) {
 34617	      if (iy != 0) {
 34618	        k = j + iy;
 34619	        ipiv[j] = (int8_T)(k + 1);
 34620	        smax = b_A[j];
 34621	        b_A[j] = b_A[k];
 34622	        b_A[k] = smax;
 34623	        ix = j + 4;
 34624	        iy = k + 4;
 34625	        smax = b_A[ix];
 34626	        b_A[ix] = b_A[iy];
 34627	        b_A[iy] = smax;
 34628	        ix += 4;
 34629	        iy += 4;
 34630	        smax = b_A[ix];
 34631	        b_A[ix] = b_A[iy];
 34632	        b_A[iy] = smax;
 34633	        ix += 4;
 34634	        iy += 4;
 34635	        smax = b_A[ix];
 34636	        b_A[ix] = b_A[iy];
 34637	        b_A[iy] = smax;
 34638	      }
 34639	
 34640	      iy = (ip - j) + 4;
 34641	      for (ix = ip + 1; ix < iy; ix++) {
 34642	        b_A[ix] /= b_A[ip];
 34643	      }
 34644	    }
 34645	
 34646	    iy = ip + 5;
 34647	    ix = ip + 4;
 34648	    for (k = 0; k <= 2 - j; k++) {
 34649	      smax = b_A[ix];
 34650	      if (b_A[ix] != 0.0) {
 34651	        c_ix = ip + 1;
 34652	        d = (iy - j) + 3;
 34653	        for (ijA = iy; ijA < d; ijA++) {
 34654	          b_A[ijA] += b_A[c_ix] * -smax;
 34655	          c_ix++;
 34656	        }
 34657	      }
 34658	
 34659	      ix += 4;
 34660	      iy += 4;
 34661	    }
 34662	  }
 34663	
 34664	  for (j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
 34665	    if (j + 1 != ipiv[j]) {
 34666	      ip = ipiv[j] - 1;
 34667	      smax = B[j];
 34668	      B[j] = B[ip];
 34669	      B[ip] = smax;
 34670	      smax = B[j + 4];
 34671	      B[j + 4] = B[ip + 4];
 34672	      B[ip + 4] = smax;
 34673	      smax = B[j + 8];
 34674	      B[j + 8] = B[ip + 8];
 34675	      B[ip + 8] = smax;
 34676	      smax = B[j + 12];
 34677	      B[j + 12] = B[ip + 12];
 34678	      B[ip + 12] = smax;
 34679	    }
 34680	  }
 34681	
 34682	  for (j = 0; j < 4; j++) {
 34683	    ix = j << 2;
 34684	    if (B[ix] != 0.0) {
 34685	      for (k = 2; k < 5; k++) {
 34686	        ip = (k + ix) - 1;
 34687	        B[ip] -= b_A[k - 1] * B[ix];
 34688	      }
 34689	    }
 34690	
 34691	    if (B[1 + ix] != 0.0) {
 34692	      for (k = 3; k < 5; k++) {
 34693	        ip = (k + ix) - 1;
 34694	        B[ip] -= B[1 + ix] * b_A[k + 3];
 34695	      }
 34696	    }
 34697	
 34698	    smax = B[2 + ix];
 34699	    if (smax != 0.0) {
 34700	      B[ix + 3] -= smax * b_A[11];
 34701	    }
 34702	  }
 34703	
 34704	  for (j = 0; j < 4; j++) {
 34705	    ip = j << 2;
 34706	    smax = B[3 + ip];
 34707	    if (smax != 0.0) {
 34708	      B[3 + ip] = smax / b_A[15];
 34709	      for (k = 0; k < 3; k++) {
 34710	        ix = k + ip;
 34711	        B[ix] -= B[3 + ip] * b_A[k + 12];
 34712	      }
 34713	    }
 34714	
 34715	    smax = B[2 + ip];
 34716	    if (smax != 0.0) {
 34717	      B[2 + ip] = smax / b_A[10];
 34718	      for (k = 0; k < 2; k++) {
 34719	        ix = k + ip;
 34720	        B[ix] -= B[2 + ip] * b_A[k + 8];
 34721	      }
 34722	    }
 34723	
 34724	    smax = B[1 + ip];
 34725	    if (smax != 0.0) {
 34726	      B[1 + ip] = smax / b_A[5];
 34727	      B[ip] -= B[1 + ip] * b_A[4];
 34728	    }
 34729	
 34730	    if (B[ip] != 0.0) {
 34731	      B[ip] /= b_A[0];
 34732	    }
 34733	  }
 34734	}

 34736	real_T Ccontroller_ballcatcher_inv_kin::rt_atan2d_snf (real_T u0, real_T u1)
 34737	{
 34738	  real_T y;
 34739	  int32_T u0_0;
 34740	  int32_T u1_0;
 34741	  if (rtIsNaN(u0) || rtIsNaN(u1)) {
 34742	    y = (rtNaN);
 34743	  } else if (rtIsInf(u0) && rtIsInf(u1)) {
 34744	    if (u0 > 0.0) {
 34745	      u0_0 = 1;
 34746	    } else {
 34747	      u0_0 = -1;
 34748	    }
 34749	
 34750	    if (u1 > 0.0) {
 34751	      u1_0 = 1;
 34752	    } else {
 34753	      u1_0 = -1;
 34754	    }
 34755	
 34756	    y = atan2((real_T)u0_0, (real_T)u1_0);
 34757	  } else if (u1 == 0.0) {
 34758	    if (u0 > 0.0) {
 34759	      y = RT_PI / 2.0;
 34760	    } else if (u0 < 0.0) {
 34761	      y = -(RT_PI / 2.0);
 34762	    } else {
 34763	      y = 0.0;
 34764	    }
 34765	  } else {
 34766	    y = atan2(u0, u1);
 34767	  }
 34768	
 34769	  return y;
 34770	}

 34796	void Ccontroller_ballcatcher_inv_kin::controller_ballcatcher_inv_kin_mod (const real_T x_data[], const int32_T *x_size, real_T r_data[], int32_T *r_size)

 34798	  real_T z1_data[119];
 34799	  real_T b_r;
 34800	  boolean_T rEQ0;
 34801	  real_T q;
 34802	  int32_T loop_ub;

 34805	  if (0 <= x_idx_0 - 1) {
 34806	    memcpy(&z1_data[0], &r_data[0], x_idx_0 * sizeof(real_T));

 34810	    if ((!rtIsInf(x_data[loop_ub])) && (!rtIsNaN(x_data[loop_ub]))) {

 34815	        rEQ0 = (b_r == 0.0);

 34817	          q = std::abs(x_data[loop_ub] / 6.2831853071795862);
 34818	          rEQ0 = (std::abs(q - std::floor(q + 0.5)) <= 2.2204460492503131E-16 *
 34819	                  q);
 34820	        }
 34821	
 34822	        if (rEQ0) {
 34823	          b_r = 0.0;
 34824	        } else {
 34825	          if (x_data[loop_ub] < 0.0) {
 34826	            b_r += 6.2831853071795862;
 34827	          }
 34828	        }
 34829	      }
 34830	    } else {
 34831	      b_r = (rtNaN);
 34832	    }
 34833

 34835	  }
 34836	
 34837	  *r_size = (int8_T)*x_size;
 34838	  if (0 <= x_idx_0 - 1) {
